					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Here's another try. This time I resized to 128 high, boosted saturation to +75%, boosted constrast +40%, lightened the eyes and nose, made a special 4 color swatch set by eyedropping on 4 places on the canvas (note, these are not the final colors), mode/indexed color, use the custom swatch as the palette, dither 40%. touched up the eyes again with pencil tool.<br /><br />copy. paste into YY-CHR. It looks nicer with at least 1 complementary color.</div>

					
